SPORT: Clwb Rygbi - Zebre v Cardiff Blues
On: S4C Digital    
Date: Sunday 7th September 2014 
Time: 15:45 to 18:00 

At the start of the Guiness Pro12 season, join Gareth Roberts and the Clwb Rygbi team for live coverage of Zebre v Blues at the Stadio XXV Aprile. The Blues will be keen to strike back after losing twice to the Italian side last season, leading to the resignation of their Performance Director, Phil Davies.
English red button commentary.
